      "planinhalt": "<p data-ogsb=\"white\">The technologies covered in this module are:</p>\n<p data-ogsb=\"white\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ogsb=\"white\">Network Automation Tools</li>\n<li data-ogsb=\"white\">Network Automation Frameworks (e.g.: in Python)</li>\n<li data-ogsb=\"white\">Event/Model-Driven Automation</li>\n<li data-ogsb=\"white\">Network APIs</li>\n<li data-ogsb=\"white\">Single Source of Truth</li>\n<li data-ogsb=\"white\">CI/CD for Network Automation</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This module is mainly practically oriented.&nbsp; It is completely in English. Bilateral questions can be in German as well. &nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>*50% of the grade is derived from the projects through the semester, and the remaining 50% from the written exam.&nbsp;</p>",
